                          "script": "\tpage \u003d \u0027/hmi/cncloader/recipeselection\u0027\n\tstatus \u003d self.view.custom.status\n\treason \u003d self.view.custom.selectedReason\n\tif status \u003d\u003d 1:\n#\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Good\u0027)\n\t\tstatus \u003d \u0027Good\u0027\n\t\tself.session.custom.rerun \u003d False\n\t\tself.session.custom.selectedCylinders \u003d []\n\t\tself.session.custom.selectedData \u003d {}\n\t\tself.session.custom.selectedBore \u003d 0\n\t\tself.session.custom.selectedMill \u003d 0\n#\t\tsystem.perspective.navigate(page)\n\telif status \u003d\u003d 2:\n\t\tif reason !\u003d 0:\n#\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Bad\u0027)\n\t\t\tstatus \u003d \u0027Bad\u0027\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.rerun \u003d False\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.selectedCylinders \u003d []\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.selectedData \u003d {}\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.selectedBore \u003d 0\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.selectedMill \u003d 0\n#\t\t\tsystem.perspective.navigate(page)\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Select a reason\u0027)\n\telif status \u003d\u003d 3:\n\t\tif reason !\u003d 0:\n#\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Re-run\u0027)\n\t\t\tstatus \u003d \u0027Re-run\u0027\n\t\t\tself.session.custom.rerun \u003d True\n#\t\t\tsystem.perspective.navigate(page)\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\u0027Select a reason\u0027)\n\telse:\n\t\tpass\n\t\t\n\tdata \u003d {\n\t\t\u0027status\u0027 : status,\n\t\t\u0027reasonUUID\u0027 :reason,\n\t\t\u0027user\u0027:self.session.props.auth.user.userName}\n\tresp \u003d BlueRidge.HMI.CNCLoader.RunResult.add(data)\n\tsystem.perspective.navigate(page)"
